OL,6,FAn 84-year-old man has been charged in
OL,7,Fconnection with the death of a woman
OL,8,Fin the Scottish Borders.
OL,10,FMargaret Maude Hanson, also 84, from
OL,11,FGalashiels, was pronounced dead at a
OL,12,Fproperty on Wood Street after Police
OL,13,FScotland received reports of her death
OL,14,Fjust after 3:05am on 9 December 2024.
OL,16,FIn a statement, the 84-year-old's
OL,17,Ffamily said: "We are devastated at the
OL,18,Floss of our mum and gran.
