OL,6,F"Margaret will be sorely missed by all
OL,7,Fwho knew and loved her. We would ask
OL,8,Fthat our privacy is respected at this
OL,9,Fvery difficult time."
OL,11,FThe 84-year-old man arrested and
OL,12,Fcharged in connection to Ms Hanson is
OL,13,Fdue to appear at Selkirk Sheriff Court
OL,14,Fon 10 December 2024.
OL,16,FDebbie Duncan, Police Scotland
OL,17,FDetective Inspector, said: "Our
OL,18,Fthoughts remain with the family and
OL,19,Ffriends of Margaret who are being
OL,20,Fsupported by specialist officers.
